name: Caldwell - Gibraltar - Perfecto
additionalNotes: The Caldwell Gibraltar is one of three cigars in the Selección Junior Varsity line and this Varsity Line is a more budget friendly line from Caldwell. All the cigars in the Selección Junior Varsity line have a theme based around Spain. The Gibraltar, which is named for the island off the Iberian Peninsula, is a Dominican Habano offering. The construction is spot-on, and when we tried them, we were suitably impressed by the flavor for a medium-bodied cigar. There are woody and leathery notes, accompanied by sweet spices and a peppery finish.
